  "title": "Melting Rich Kenyan Sevaiiya Pasta",
  "description": "A rich and cheesy Kenyan dish featuring sevaiiya, perfect for a date night, with confit tomato and pescatarian friendly ingredients, served in a tagliere vessel.",
