  "instructions": [
    "Bring a large pot of salted water to a boil and cook the sevaiiya according to package instructions until al dente.",
    "In a large skillet, heat the olive oil over medium heat and saute the garlic until fragrant.",
    "Add the confit tomato to the skillet and stir to combine.",
    "In a large bowl, combine the cooked sevaiiya, confit tomato mixture, and grated grana padano cheese.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Transfer the sevaiiya mixture to a tagliere vessel and top with chopped basil.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy.",
    "Garnish with additional basil if desired."
